76IDBTransaction::IDBTransaction(IDBDatabase& database, const IDBTransactionInfo& info, IDBOpenDBRequest* request)
77 : IDBActiveDOMObject(database.scriptExecutionContext())
78 , m_database(database)
79 , m_info(info)
80 , m_openDBRequest(request)
81 , m_currentlyCompletingRequest(request)
82
83{
84 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::IDBTransaction - %s", m_info.loggingString().utf8().data());
85 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
86
87 ++numberOfIDBTransactions;
88
89 if (m_info.mode() == IDBTransactionMode::Versionchange) {
90 ASSERT(m_openDBRequest);
91 m_openDBRequest->setVersionChangeTransaction(*this);
92 m_startedOnServer = true;
93 } else {
94 activate();
95
96 auto* context = scriptExecutionContext();
97 ASSERT(context);
98
99 context->eventLoop().runAtEndOfMicrotaskCheckpoint([protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] {
100 protectedThis->deactivate();
101 });
102
103 establishOnServer();
104 }
105
106 suspendIfNeeded();
107}
108
109IDBTransaction::~IDBTransaction()
110{
111 --numberOfIDBTransactions;
112 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
113}

117 return m_database->connectionProxy();

120Ref<DOMStringList> IDBTransaction::objectStoreNames() const
121{
122 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
123
124 const Vector<String> names = isVersionChange() ? m_database->info().objectStoreNames() : m_info.objectStores();
125
126 Ref<DOMStringList> objectStoreNames = DOMStringList::create();
127 for (auto& name : names)
128 objectStoreNames->append(name);
129
130 objectStoreNames->sort();
131 return objectStoreNames;
132}

146ExceptionOr<Ref<IDBObjectStore>> IDBTransaction::objectStore(const String& objectStoreName)
147{
148 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::objectStore");
149 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
150
151 if (!scriptExecutionContext())
152 return Exception { InvalidStateError };
153
154 if (isFinishedOrFinishing())
155 return Exception { InvalidStateError, "Failed to execute 'objectStore' on 'IDBTransaction': The transaction finished."_s };
156
157 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
158
159 if (auto* store = m_referencedObjectStores.get(objectStoreName))
160 return makeRef(*store);
161
162 bool found = false;
163 for (auto& objectStore : m_info.objectStores()) {
164 if (objectStore == objectStoreName) {
165 found = true;
166 break;
167 }
168 }
169
170 auto* info = m_database->info().infoForExistingObjectStore(objectStoreName);
171 if (!info)
172 return Exception { NotFoundError, "Failed to execute 'objectStore' on 'IDBTransaction': The specified object store was not found."_s };
173
174 // Version change transactions are scoped to every object store in the database.
175 if (!info || (!found && !isVersionChange()))
176 return Exception { NotFoundError, "Failed to execute 'objectStore' on 'IDBTransaction': The specified object store was not found."_s };
177
178 auto objectStore = makeUnique<IDBObjectStore>(*scriptExecutionContext(), *info, *this);
179 auto* rawObjectStore = objectStore.get();
180 m_referencedObjectStores.set(objectStoreName, WTFMove(objectStore));
181
182 return Ref<IDBObjectStore>(*rawObjectStore);
183}

203 m_state = state;

207ExceptionOr<void> IDBTransaction::abort()
208{
209 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::abort");
210 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
211
212 if (isFinishedOrFinishing())
213 return Exception { InvalidStateError, "Failed to execute 'abort' on 'IDBTransaction': The transaction is inactive or finished."_s };
214
215 internalAbort();
216
217 return { };
218}
219
220void IDBTransaction::internalAbort()
221{
222 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::internalAbort");
223 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
224 ASSERT(!isFinishedOrFinishing());
225
226 m_database->willAbortTransaction(*this);
227
228 if (isVersionChange()) {
229 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
230
231 auto& info = m_database->info();
232 Vector<uint64_t> identifiersToRemove;
233 Vector<std::unique_ptr<IDBObjectStore>> objectStoresToDelete;
234 for (auto& iterator : m_deletedObjectStores) {
235 if (info.infoForExistingObjectStore(iterator.key)) {
236 auto name = iterator.value->info().name();
237 auto result = m_referencedObjectStores.add(name, nullptr);
238 if (!result.isNewEntry)
239 objectStoresToDelete.append(std::exchange(result.iterator->value, nullptr));
240 result.iterator->value = std::exchange(iterator.value, nullptr);
241 identifiersToRemove.append(iterator.key);
242 }
243 }
244
245 for (auto identifier : identifiersToRemove)
246 m_deletedObjectStores.remove(identifier);
247
248 for (auto& objectStore : m_referencedObjectStores.values())
249 objectStore->rollbackForVersionChangeAbort();
250
251 for (auto& objectStore : objectStoresToDelete) {
252 objectStore->rollbackForVersionChangeAbort();
253 auto objectStoreIdentifier = objectStore->info().identifier();
254 m_deletedObjectStores.set(objectStoreIdentifier, std::exchange(objectStore, nullptr));
255 }
256 }
257
258 transitionedToFinishing(IndexedDB::TransactionState::Aborting);
259
260 m_abortQueue.swap(m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue);
261
262 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB abort-on-server operation: Transaction %s", info().identifier().loggingString().utf8().data());
263 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, nullptr, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (auto& operation) {
264 protectedThis->abortOnServerAndCancelRequests(operation);
265 }));
266}
267
268void IDBTransaction::abortInProgressOperations(const IDBError& error)
269{
270 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::abortInProgressOperations");
271
272 Vector<RefPtr<IDBClient::TransactionOperation>> inProgressAbortVector;
273 inProgressAbortVector.reserveInitialCapacity(m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.size());
274 while (!m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.isEmpty())
275 inProgressAbortVector.uncheckedAppend(m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.takeFirst());
276
277 for (auto& operation : inProgressAbortVector) {
278 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.append(operation.get());
279 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
280 operation->doComplete(IDBResultData::error(operation->identifier(), error));
281 }
282
283 m_transactionOperationResultMap.clear();
284
285 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
286 connectionProxy().forgetActiveOperations(inProgressAbortVector);
287}
288
289void IDBTransaction::abortOnServerAndCancelRequests(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation)
290{
291 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::abortOnServerAndCancelRequests");
292 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
293 ASSERT(m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue.isEmpty());
294
295 m_database->connectionProxy().abortTransaction(*this);
296
297 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationMap.contains(operation.identifier()));
298 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.last() == &operation);
299 m_transactionOperationMap.remove(operation.identifier());
300 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.removeLast();
301
302 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
303
304 IDBError error(AbortError);
305
306 abortInProgressOperations(error);
307
308 for (auto& operation : m_abortQueue) {
309 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.append(operation.get());
310 operation->doComplete(IDBResultData::error(operation->identifier(), error));
311 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
312 }
313
314 m_abortQueue.clear();
315 m_openRequests.clear();
316 // Since we're aborting, it should be impossible to have queued any further operations.
317 ASSERT(m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue.isEmpty());
318}

332void IDBTransaction::stop()
333{
334 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::stop - %s", m_info.loggingString().utf8().data());
335 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
336
337 // IDBDatabase::stop() calls IDBTransaction::stop() for each of its active transactions.
338 // Since the order of calling ActiveDOMObject::stop() is random, we might already have been stopped.
339 if (m_isStopped)
340 return;
341
342 removeAllEventListeners();
343
344 m_isStopped = true;
345
346 if (isVersionChange())
347 m_openDBRequest = nullptr;
348
349 if (isFinishedOrFinishing())
350 return;
351
352 internalAbort();
353}
354
355bool IDBTransaction::isActive() const
356{
357 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
358 return m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Active;
359}
360
361bool IDBTransaction::isFinishedOrFinishing() const
362{
363 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
364
365 return m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Committing
366 || m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Aborting
367 || m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Finished;
368}

370void IDBTransaction::addRequest(IDBRequest& request)
371{
372 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
373 m_openRequests.add(&request);
374}
375
376void IDBTransaction::removeRequest(IDBRequest& request)
377{
378 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
379 if (m_currentlyCompletingRequest == &request)
380 return;
381
382 m_openRequests.remove(&request);
383
384 autoCommit();
385}

387void IDBTransaction::scheduleOperation(Ref<IDBClient::TransactionOperation>&& operation, IsWriteOperation isWriteOperation)
388{
389 ASSERT(!m_transactionOperationMap.contains(operation->identifier()));
390 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
391
392 if (isWriteOperation == IsWriteOperation::Yes)
393 m_lastWriteOperationID = operation->operationID();
394
395 auto identifier = operation->identifier();
396 m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue.append(operation.copyRef());
397 m_transactionOperationMap.set(identifier, WTFMove(operation));
398
399 handlePendingOperations();
400}
401
402void IDBTransaction::operationCompletedOnServer(const IDBResultData& data, IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation)
403{
404 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
405 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(operation.originThread()));
406
407 if (!m_transactionOperationMap.contains(operation.identifier()))
408 return;
409
410 m_transactionOperationResultMap.set(&operation, IDBResultData(data));
411
412 if (!m_currentlyCompletingRequest)
413 handleOperationsCompletedOnServer();
414}
415
416void IDBTransaction::handleOperationsCompletedOnServer()
417{
418 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::handleOperationsCompletedOnServer");
419 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
420
421 while (!m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.isEmpty() && !m_currentlyCompletingRequest) {
422 RefPtr<IDBClient::TransactionOperation> currentOperation = m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.first();
423 if (!m_transactionOperationResultMap.contains(currentOperation))
424 return;
425
426 currentOperation->doComplete(m_transactionOperationResultMap.take(currentOperation));
427 }
428}

430void IDBTransaction::completeNoncursorRequest(IDBRequest& request, const IDBResultData& result)
431{
432 ASSERT(!m_currentlyCompletingRequest);
433
434 request.completeRequestAndDispatchEvent(result);
435
436 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = &request;
437}
438
439void IDBTransaction::completeCursorRequest(IDBRequest& request, const IDBResultData& result)
440{
441 ASSERT(!m_currentlyCompletingRequest);
442
443 request.didOpenOrIterateCursor(result);
444
445 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = &request;
446}
447
448void IDBTransaction::finishedDispatchEventForRequest(IDBRequest& request)
449{
450 if (isFinished())
451 return;
452
453 ASSERT_UNUSED(request, !m_currentlyCompletingRequest || m_currentlyCompletingRequest == &request);
454
455 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
456 handleOperationsCompletedOnServer();
457}

459void IDBTransaction::commit()
460{
461 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::commit");
462 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
463 ASSERT(!isFinishedOrFinishing());
464
465 transitionedToFinishing(IndexedDB::TransactionState::Committing);
466 m_database->willCommitTransaction(*this);
467
468 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB commit operation: Transaction %s", info().identifier().loggingString().utf8().data());
469 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, nullptr, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (auto& operation) {
470 protectedThis->commitOnServer(operation);
471 }));
472}
473
474void IDBTransaction::commitOnServer(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation)
475{
476 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::commitOnServer");
477 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
478
479 m_database->connectionProxy().commitTransaction(*this);
480
481 ASSERT(!m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.isEmpty());
482 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.last() == &operation);
483 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.removeLast();
484
485 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationMap.contains(operation.identifier()));
486 m_transactionOperationMap.remove(operation.identifier());
487}
488
489void IDBTransaction::finishAbortOrCommit()
490{
491 ASSERT(m_state != IndexedDB::TransactionState::Finished);
492 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
493
494 m_state = IndexedDB::TransactionState::Finished;
495}
496
497void IDBTransaction::didStart(const IDBError& error)
498{
499 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didStart");
500 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
501
502 m_database->didStartTransaction(*this);
503
504 m_startedOnServer = true;
505
506 // It's possible the transaction failed to start on the server.
507 // That equates to an abort.
508 if (!error.isNull()) {
509 didAbort(error);
510 return;
511 }
512
513 handlePendingOperations();
514
515 // It's possible transaction does not create requests (or creates but finishes them early
516 // because of error) during intialization. In this case, since the transaction will
517 // not be active any more, we can end it.
518 autoCommit();
519}
520
521void IDBTransaction::notifyDidAbort(const IDBError& error)
522{
523 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
524
525 m_database->didAbortTransaction(*this);
526 m_idbError = error;
527 fireOnAbort();
528
529 if (isVersionChange() && !isContextStopped()) {
530 ASSERT(m_openDBRequest);
531 m_openDBRequest->fireErrorAfterVersionChangeCompletion();
532 }
533}
534
535void IDBTransaction::didAbort(const IDBError& error)
536{
537 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didAbort");
538 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
539
540 if (m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Finished)
541 return;
542
543 notifyDidAbort(error);
544
545 finishAbortOrCommit();
546}
547
548void IDBTransaction::didCommit(const IDBError& error)
549{
550 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didCommit");
551 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
552 ASSERT(m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Committing);
553
554 if (error.isNull()) {
555 m_database->didCommitTransaction(*this);
556 fireOnComplete();
557 } else {
558 m_database->willAbortTransaction(*this);
559 notifyDidAbort(error);
560 }
561
562 finishAbortOrCommit();
563}
564
565void IDBTransaction::fireOnComplete()
566{
567 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::fireOnComplete");
568 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
569 enqueueEvent(Event::create(eventNames().completeEvent, Event::CanBubble::No, Event::IsCancelable::No));
570}
571
572void IDBTransaction::fireOnAbort()
573{
574 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::fireOnAbort");
575 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
576 enqueueEvent(Event::create(eventNames().abortEvent, Event::CanBubble::Yes, Event::IsCancelable::No));
577}
578
579void IDBTransaction::enqueueEvent(Ref<Event>&& event)
580{
581 ASSERT(m_state != IndexedDB::TransactionState::Finished);
582 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
583
584 if (!scriptExecutionContext() || isContextStopped())
585 return;
586
587 m_abortOrCommitEvent = event.ptr();
588 queueTaskToDispatchEvent(*this, TaskSource::DatabaseAccess, WTFMove(event));
589}
590
591void IDBTransaction::dispatchEvent(Event& event)
592{
593 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::dispatchEvent");
594
595 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
596 ASSERT(scriptExecutionContext());
597 ASSERT(!isContextStopped());
598
599
600 auto protectedThis = makeRef(*this);
601
602 EventDispatcher::dispatchEvent({ this, m_database.ptr() }, event);
603
604 if (m_abortOrCommitEvent != &event)
605 return;
606
607 ASSERT(event.type() == eventNames().completeEvent || event.type() == eventNames().abortEvent);
608 m_didDispatchAbortOrCommit = true;
609
610 if (isVersionChange()) {
611 m_openDBRequest->versionChangeTransactionDidFinish();
612
613 if (event.type() == eventNames().completeEvent) {
614 if (m_database->isClosingOrClosed())
615 m_openDBRequest->fireErrorAfterVersionChangeCompletion();
616 else
617 m_openDBRequest->fireSuccessAfterVersionChangeCommit();
618 }
619
620 m_openDBRequest = nullptr;
621 }
622}

624Ref<IDBObjectStore> IDBTransaction::createObjectStore(const IDBObjectStoreInfo& info)
625{
626 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::createObjectStore");
627 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
628 ASSERT(scriptExecutionContext());
629 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
630
631 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
632
633 auto objectStore = makeUnique<IDBObjectStore>(*scriptExecutionContext(), info, *this);
634 auto* rawObjectStore = objectStore.get();
635 m_referencedObjectStores.set(info.name(), WTFMove(objectStore));
636
637 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB create object store operation: %s", info.condensedLoggingString().utf8().data());
638 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (const auto& result) {
639 protectedThis->didCreateObjectStoreOnServer(result);
640 }, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), info = info.isolatedCopy()] (auto& operation) {
641 protectedThis->createObjectStoreOnServer(operation, info);
642 }), IsWriteOperation::Yes);
643
644 return *rawObjectStore;
645}

647void IDBTransaction::createObjectStoreOnServer(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation, const IDBObjectStoreInfo& info)
648{
649 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::createObjectStoreOnServer");
650 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
651 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
652
653 m_database->connectionProxy().createObjectStore(operation, info);
654}

656void IDBTransaction::didCreateObjectStoreOnServer(const IDBResultData& resultData)
657{
658 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didCreateObjectStoreOnServer");
659 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
660 ASSERT_UNUSED(resultData, resultData.type() == IDBResultType::CreateObjectStoreSuccess || resultData.type() == IDBResultType::Error);
661}
662
663void IDBTransaction::renameObjectStore(IDBObjectStore& objectStore, const String& newName)
664{
665 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::renameObjectStore");
666
667 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
668
669 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
670 ASSERT(scriptExecutionContext());
671 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
672
673 ASSERT(m_referencedObjectStores.contains(objectStore.info().name()));
674 ASSERT(!m_referencedObjectStores.contains(newName));
675 ASSERT(m_referencedObjectStores.get(objectStore.info().name()) == &objectStore);
676
677 uint64_t objectStoreIdentifier = objectStore.info().identifier();
678
679 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB rename object store operation: %s to %s", objectStore.info().condensedLoggingString().utf8().data(), newName.utf8().data());
680 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (const auto& result) {
681 protectedThis->didRenameObjectStoreOnServer(result);
682 }, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), objectStoreIdentifier, newName = newName.isolatedCopy()] (auto& operation) {
683 protectedThis->renameObjectStoreOnServer(operation, objectStoreIdentifier, newName);
684 }), IsWriteOperation::Yes);
685
686 m_referencedObjectStores.set(newName, m_referencedObjectStores.take(objectStore.info().name()));
687}
688
689void IDBTransaction::renameObjectStoreOnServer(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation, const uint64_t& objectStoreIdentifier, const String& newName)
690{
691 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::renameObjectStoreOnServer");
692 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
693 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
694
695 m_database->connectionProxy().renameObjectStore(operation, objectStoreIdentifier, newName);
696}

698void IDBTransaction::didRenameObjectStoreOnServer(const IDBResultData& resultData)
699{
700 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didRenameObjectStoreOnServer");
701 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
702 ASSERT_UNUSED(resultData, resultData.type() == IDBResultType::RenameObjectStoreSuccess || resultData.type() == IDBResultType::Error);
703}
704
705std::unique_ptr<IDBIndex> IDBTransaction::createIndex(IDBObjectStore& objectStore, const IDBIndexInfo& info)
706{
707 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::createIndex");
708 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
709 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
710
711 if (!scriptExecutionContext())
712 return nullptr;
713
714 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB create index operation: %s under object store %s", info.condensedLoggingString().utf8().data(), objectStore.info().condensedLoggingString().utf8().data());
715 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (const auto& result) {
716 protectedThis->didCreateIndexOnServer(result);
717 }, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), info = info.isolatedCopy()] (auto& operation) {
718 protectedThis->createIndexOnServer(operation, info);
719 }), IsWriteOperation::Yes);
720
721 return makeUnique<IDBIndex>(*scriptExecutionContext(), info, objectStore);
722}
723
724void IDBTransaction::createIndexOnServer(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation, const IDBIndexInfo& info)
725{
726 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::createIndexOnServer");
727 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
728 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
729
730 m_database->connectionProxy().createIndex(operation, info);
731}
732
733void IDBTransaction::didCreateIndexOnServer(const IDBResultData& resultData)
734{
735 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didCreateIndexOnServer");
736 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
737
738 if (resultData.type() == IDBResultType::CreateIndexSuccess)
739 return;
740
741 ASSERT(resultData.type() == IDBResultType::Error);
742
743 // This operation might have failed because the transaction is already aborting.
744 if (m_state == IndexedDB::TransactionState::Aborting)
745 return;
746
747 // Otherwise, failure to create an index forced abortion of the transaction.
748 abortDueToFailedRequest(DOMException::create(resultData.error().message(), resultData.error().name()));
749}

751void IDBTransaction::renameIndex(IDBIndex& index, const String& newName)
752{
753 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::renameIndex");
754 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
755
756 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
757 ASSERT(scriptExecutionContext());
758 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
759
760 ASSERT(m_referencedObjectStores.contains(index.objectStore().info().name()));
761 ASSERT(m_referencedObjectStores.get(index.objectStore().info().name()) == &index.objectStore());
762
763 index.objectStore().renameReferencedIndex(index, newName);
764
765 uint64_t objectStoreIdentifier = index.objectStore().info().identifier();
766 uint64_t indexIdentifier = index.info().identifier();
767
768 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB rename index operation: %s to %s under object store %" PRIu64, index.info().condensedLoggingString().utf8().data(), newName.utf8().data(), index.info().objectStoreIdentifier());
769 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (const auto& result) {
770 protectedThis->didRenameIndexOnServer(result);
771 }, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), objectStoreIdentifier, indexIdentifier, newName = newName.isolatedCopy()] (auto& operation) {
772 protectedThis->renameIndexOnServer(operation, objectStoreIdentifier, indexIdentifier, newName);
773 }), IsWriteOperation::Yes);
774}

867// FIXME: changes here
868void IDBTransaction::iterateCursorOnServer(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation, const IDBIterateCursorData& data)
869{
870 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::iterateCursorOnServer");
871 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
872 ASSERT(operation.idbRequest());
873
874 auto* cursor = operation.idbRequest()->pendingCursor();
875 ASSERT(cursor);
876
877 if (data.keyData.isNull() && data.primaryKeyData.isNull()) {
878 if (auto getResult = cursor->iterateWithPrefetchedRecords(data.count, m_lastWriteOperationID)) {
879 auto result = IDBResultData::iterateCursorSuccess(operation.identifier(), getResult.value());
880 m_database->connectionProxy().iterateCursor(operation, { data.keyData, data.primaryKeyData, data.count, IndexedDB::CursorIterateOption::DoNotReply });
881 operationCompletedOnServer(result, operation);
882 return;
883 }
884 }
885
886 cursor->clearPrefetchedRecords();
887
888 ASSERT(data.option == IndexedDB::CursorIterateOption::Reply);
889 m_database->connectionProxy().iterateCursor(operation, data);
890}

954void IDBTransaction::didGetAllRecordsOnServer(IDBRequest& request, const IDBResultData& resultData)
955{
956 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didGetAllRecordsOnServer");
957 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
958
959 if (resultData.type() == IDBResultType::Error) {
960 completeNoncursorRequest(request, resultData);
961 return;
962 }
963
964 ASSERT(resultData.type() == IDBResultType::GetAllRecordsSuccess);
965
966 auto& getAllResult = resultData.getAllResult();
967 switch (getAllResult.type()) {
968 case IndexedDB::GetAllType::Keys:
969 request.setResult(getAllResult.keys());
970 break;
971 case IndexedDB::GetAllType::Values:
972 request.setResult(getAllResult);
973 break;
974 }
975
976 completeNoncursorRequest(request, resultData);
977}

1050
1051void IDBTransaction::didGetRecordOnServer(IDBRequest& request, const IDBResultData& resultData)
1052{
1053 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didGetRecordOnServer");
1054 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
1055
1056 if (resultData.type() == IDBResultType::Error) {
1057 completeNoncursorRequest(request, resultData);
1058 return;
1059 }
1060
1061 ASSERT(resultData.type() == IDBResultType::GetRecordSuccess);
1062
1063 bool useResultKey = request.sourceIndexIdentifier() && request.requestedIndexRecordType() == IndexedDB::IndexRecordType::Key;
1064 if (!useResultKey)
1065 useResultKey = request.requestedObjectStoreRecordType() == IndexedDB::ObjectStoreRecordType::KeyOnly;
1066
1067 const IDBGetResult& result = resultData.getResult();
1068
1069 if (useResultKey) {
1070 if (!result.keyData().isNull())
1071 request.setResult(result.keyData());
1072 else
1073 request.setResultToUndefined();
1074 } else {
1075 if (resultData.getResult().value().data().data())
1076 request.setResultToStructuredClone(resultData.getResult());
1077 else
1078 request.setResultToUndefined();
1079 }
1080
1081 completeNoncursorRequest(request, resultData);
1082}

1246void IDBTransaction::putOrAddOnServer(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation, RefPtr<IDBKey> key, RefPtr<SerializedScriptValue> value, const IndexedDB::ObjectStoreOverwriteMode& overwriteMode)
1247{
1248 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::putOrAddOnServer");
1249 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(originThread()));
1250 ASSERT(!isReadOnly());
1251 ASSERT(value);
1252
1253 if (!value->hasBlobURLs()) {
1254 m_database->connectionProxy().putOrAdd(operation, key.get(), *value, overwriteMode);
1255 return;
1256 }
1257
1258 // Due to current limitations on our ability to post tasks back to a worker thread,
1259 // workers currently write blobs to disk synchronously.
1260 // FIXME: https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=157958 - Make this asynchronous after refactoring allows it.
1261 if (!isMainThread()) {
1262 auto idbValue = value->writeBlobsToDiskForIndexedDBSynchronously();
1263 if (idbValue.data().data())
1264 m_database->connectionProxy().putOrAdd(operation, key.get(), idbValue, overwriteMode);
1265 else {
1266 // If the IDBValue doesn't have any data, then something went wrong writing the blobs to disk.
1267 // In that case, we cannot successfully store this record, so we callback with an error.
1268 RefPtr<IDBClient::TransactionOperation> protectedOperation(&operation);
1269 auto result = IDBResultData::error(operation.identifier(), IDBError { UnknownError, "Error preparing Blob/File data to be stored in object store"_s });
1270 scriptExecutionContext()->postTask([protectedOperation = WTFMove(protectedOperation), result = WTFMove(result)](ScriptExecutionContext&) {
1271 protectedOperation->doComplete(result);
1272 });
1273 }
1274 return;
1275 }
1276
1277 // Since this request won't actually go to the server until the blob writes are complete,
1278 // stop future requests from going to the server ahead of it.
1279 operation.setNextRequestCanGoToServer(false);
1280
1281 value->writeBlobsToDiskForIndexedDB([protectedThis = makeRef(*this), this, protectedOperation = Ref<IDBClient::TransactionOperation>(operation), keyData = IDBKeyData(key.get()).isolatedCopy(), overwriteMode](IDBValue&& idbValue) mutable {
1282 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(originThread()));
1283 ASSERT(isMainThread());
1284 if (idbValue.data().data()) {
1285 m_database->connectionProxy().putOrAdd(protectedOperation.get(), WTFMove(keyData), idbValue, overwriteMode);
1286 return;
1287 }
1288
1289 // If the IDBValue doesn't have any data, then something went wrong writing the blobs to disk.
1290 // In that case, we cannot successfully store this record, so we callback with an error.
1291 auto result = IDBResultData::error(protectedOperation->identifier(), IDBError { UnknownError, "Error preparing Blob/File data to be stored in object store"_s });
1292 callOnMainThread([protectedThis = WTFMove(protectedThis), protectedOperation = WTFMove(protectedOperation), result = WTFMove(result)]() mutable {
1293 protectedOperation->doComplete(result);
1294 });
1295 });
1296}

1299{
1300 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::didPutOrAddOnServer");

1310void IDBTransaction::deleteObjectStore(const String& objectStoreName)
1311{
1312 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::deleteObjectStore");
1313 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
1314 ASSERT(isVersionChange());
1315
1316 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
1317
1318 if (auto objectStore = m_referencedObjectStores.take(objectStoreName)) {
1319 objectStore->markAsDeleted();
1320 auto identifier = objectStore->info().identifier();
1321 m_deletedObjectStores.set(identifier, WTFMove(objectStore));
1322 }
1323
1324 LOG(IndexedDBOperations, "IDB delete object store operation: %s", objectStoreName.utf8().data());
1325 scheduleOperation(IDBClient::TransactionOperationImpl::create(*this, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this)] (const auto& result) {
1326 protectedThis->didDeleteObjectStoreOnServer(result);
1327 }, [protectedThis = makeRef(*this), objectStoreName = objectStoreName.isolatedCopy()] (auto& operation) {
1328 protectedThis->deleteObjectStoreOnServer(operation, objectStoreName);
1329 }), IsWriteOperation::Yes);
1330}

1378void IDBTransaction::operationCompletedOnClient(IDBClient::TransactionOperation& operation)
1379{
1380 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::operationCompletedOnClient");
1381
1382 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
1383 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(operation.originThread()));
1384 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationMap.get(operation.identifier()) == &operation);
1385 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.first() == &operation);
1386
1387 m_transactionOperationMap.remove(operation.identifier());
1388 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.removeFirst();
1389
1390 if (m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.isEmpty())
1391 handlePendingOperations();
1392
1393 autoCommit();
1394}

1423
1424void IDBTransaction::connectionClosedFromServer(const IDBError& error)
1425{
1426 LOG(IndexedDB, "IDBTransaction::connectionClosedFromServer - %s", error.message().utf8().data());
1427
1428 m_database->willAbortTransaction(*this);
1429 m_state = IndexedDB::TransactionState::Aborting;
1430
1431 // Move operations out of m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue, otherwise we may start handling
1432 // them after we forcibly complete in-progress transactions.
1433 Deque<RefPtr<IDBClient::TransactionOperation>> pendingTransactionOperationQueue;
1434 pendingTransactionOperationQueue.swap(m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue);
1435
1436 abortInProgressOperations(error);
1437
1438 auto operations = copyToVector(m_transactionOperationMap.values());
1439 for (auto& operation : operations) {
1440 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
1441 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.append(operation.get());
1442 ASSERT(m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.first() == operation.get());
1443 operation->doComplete(IDBResultData::error(operation->identifier(), error));
1444 }
1445 m_currentlyCompletingRequest = nullptr;
1446 m_openRequests.clear();
1447 pendingTransactionOperationQueue.clear();
1448
1449 connectionProxy().forgetActiveOperations(operations);
1450 connectionProxy().forgetTransaction(*this);
1451
1452 m_abortQueue.clear();
1453 m_transactionOperationMap.clear();
1454
1455 m_idbError = error;
1456 m_domError = error.toDOMException();
1457 m_database->didAbortTransaction(*this);
1458 fireOnAbort();
1459}

1461template<typename Visitor>
1462void IDBTransaction::visitReferencedObjectStores(Visitor& visitor) const
1463{
1464 Locker locker { m_referencedObjectStoreLock };
1465 for (auto& objectStore : m_referencedObjectStores.values())
1466 visitor.addOpaqueRoot(objectStore.get());
1467 for (auto& objectStore : m_deletedObjectStores.values())
1468 visitor.addOpaqueRoot(objectStore.get());
1469}

1474void IDBTransaction::handlePendingOperations()
1475{
1476 ASSERT(canCurrentThreadAccessThreadLocalData(m_database->originThread()));
1477
1478 if (!m_startedOnServer)
1479 return;
1480
1481 if (!m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.isEmpty() && !m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.last()->nextRequestCanGoToServer())
1482 return;
1483
1484 while (!m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue.isEmpty()) {
1485 auto operation = m_pendingTransactionOperationQueue.takeFirst();
1486 m_transactionOperationsInProgressQueue.append(operation.get());
1487 operation->perform();
1488
1489 if (!operation->nextRequestCanGoToServer())
1490 break;
1491 }
1492}
1493
1494void IDBTransaction::autoCommit()
1495{
1496 // If transaction is not inactive, it's active, finished or finishing.
1497 // If it's active, it may create new requests, so we cannot commit it.
1498 if (m_state != IndexedDB::TransactionState::Inactive)
1499 return;
1500
1501 if (!m_startedOnServer)
1502 return;
1503
1504 if (!m_transactionOperationMap.isEmpty())
1505 return;
1506
1507 if (!m_openRequests.isEmpty())
1508 return;
1509 ASSERT(!m_currentlyCompletingRequest);
1510
1511 commit();
1512}
